OL,6,FThe plans followed the council's
OL,7,Fapproval of the #450million
OL,8,Fdevelopment, which would see up to 700
OL,9,Fholiday lodges constructed and create
OL,10,Faround 1,200 jobs when operational.
OL,12,FThe leader of Scottish Borders
OL,13,FCouncil, Councillor Euan Jardine said:
OL,14,F"Today's decision carefully balanced
OL,15,Fconsidering the needs of Centre Parcs
OL,16,Fin making this major investment in the
OL,17,FScottish Borders, with the rights and
OL,18,Ftraditions of public access in
OL,19,FScotland.
